{
  "page": "Broken Nose",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"City Watch of King&#39;s Landing\"><img alt=\"City Watch of King&#39;s Landing.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/75/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/50px-City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/75/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/75px-City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/75/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/100px-City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Broken Nose</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"City Watch of King&#39;s Landing\"><img alt=\"City Watch of King&#39;s Landing.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/75/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/50px-City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/75/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/75px-City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/75/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/100px-City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"City Watch of King&#39;s Landing\">City Watch of King's Landing</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Broken Nose</b> is how <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a> refers to a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Gold_cloaks\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Gold cloaks\">gold cloaks</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>. His given name is unknown.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Broken_Nose&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The big guard, who has a broken nose, wears black ringmail and a golden cloak.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Broken_Nose&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Broken_Nose&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Six <a href=\"/index.php/Gold_cloaks\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Gold cloaks\">gold cloaks</a> search for <a href=\"/index.php/Gendry\" title=\"Gendry\">Gendry</a> at a village in the <a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">crownlands</a>. One of them, a big lout with a broken nose, bares his steel but is challenged by a number of <a href=\"/index.php/Yoren\" title=\"Yoren\">Yoren</a>'s recruits. Broken Nose laughs at <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a> when she enters a <a href=\"/index.php/Water_dance\" title=\"Water dance\">water dancer</a>'s pose with <a href=\"/index.php/Needle\" title=\"Needle\">Needle</a>. Yoren disarms the officer leading the gold cloaks and sends them into retreat down the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsroad\" title=\"Kingsroad\">kingsroad</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Broken_Nose&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Broken Nose</b>: You girls put away them rocks and sticks before you get spanked. None of you knows what end of a sword to hold.<br /><b>Arya</b>: I do!<br /><b>Broken Nose</b>: Put <a href=\"/index.php/Needle\" title=\"Needle\">the blade</a> away, little girl, no one wants to hurt you.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Broken Nose and <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Broken_Nose&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_5\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 5\">Chapter 5</a>, Arya II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404141834\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.068 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.259 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 481/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10546/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5758/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 595/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1060/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.180/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.5 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  249.245      1 -total\n 96.69%  240.988      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.88%  238.973      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.75%   29.277     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.50%    8.728      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.31%    5.763      3 Template:Ref\n  1.26%    3.128      3 Template:Ref/core\n  0.65%    1.610      1 Template:Quote\n  0.59%    1.480      1 Template:References\n  0.39%    0.967      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:40406-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404141834 and revision id 335365\n -->\n",
